# Always: Error Learning Trigger

If any of these happen, load skill `error-learning-1c` (and project `project-*-error-learning-agent.mdc` if present):

- `check_1c_code` / `review_1c_code` failed;
- `v8std` diagnostic appears;
- runtime/deploy/test failed;
- user invokes `capture-error` or `reflect-lesson`;
- the same mistake appears again;
- risky CFE/base-config change was attempted.

Do not create a new `.mdc` for one-off issues.  
Store: local reflection for task-only; **shared/portable lessons →** `C:\1c-shared-patterns\playbooks\agent-lessons\` + `index.md`.  
Promote to alwaysApply rule only if repeated or critical.
